"a7c4d8a63824d3f9052f0f3f68b599b6b2aeee18","tid":97642,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"你篇嘢由頭到尾都只係用緊冇/普通樣嘅高佬同好樣嘅矮仔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜撚嘢魅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試下又高又靚仔vs靚仔但矮睇下啲女仔傾向揀邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實係你篇文所講嘅所謂魅力根本冇得「培育」，因為你根本係講緊樣，而樣只能整容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而如果你講嗰啲魅力係才華，矮仔都唔會夠高佬嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為𠵱啲「魅力」係人都可以培育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到最後有才華嘅短人vs有才華嘅高佬，一樣係高佬玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77bc26d6a4234797efd525f18c19030665d305d","tid":97642,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T15:55:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ac3259b0fa9cb5f44c87ddc5fbc7b6be08c51f4","tid":97642,"uid":79275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你篇嘢由頭到尾都只係用緊冇/普通樣嘅高佬同好樣嘅矮仔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜撚嘢魅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試下又高又靚仔vs靚仔但矮睇下啲女仔傾向揀邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實係你篇文所講嘅所謂魅力根本冇得「培育」，因為你根本係講緊樣，而樣只能整容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而如果你講嗰啲魅力係才華，矮仔都唔會夠高佬嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為𠵱啲「魅力」係人都可以培育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到最後有才華嘅短人vs有才華嘅高佬，一樣係高佬玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n才華冇錯係人都可以培養，但一個人去到某個才華指標，高同矮都食到女，咁仲有需要比較高同矮邊個屈機啲？<br />\n舉例，美斯同C朗一樣係可以培養球技，佢地而家一定都受女人歡迎，你仲會比較C朗係咪因爲高多20cm 而更受女歡迎？<br />\n所以你最後個比較有才華短人vs 有才華高佬，結果應該係兩者都玩哂，而唔係高佬玩哂"},{"pid":"990aed135801ae7ca8cbe1d73de58361598d793d","tid":97642,"uid":45471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:47:06.000Z","msg":"最終咪又係睇樣，咁高有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申183"},{"pid":"727687b70dda2c2490b03f1069e7f4569ebc9948","tid":97642,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"只要你唔係矮過條女都ok嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34893ccb1669647ba5af5e42769455611bc01f5","tid":97642,"uid":25237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"靚仔就有女㗎啦 關身高咩事<br />\n利申 A0 181<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7fdc76444dd2138baeb423e37b172621d2d5fe","tid":97642,"uid":21629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T17:49:02.000Z","msg":"真係笑死人<br />\n兩個都一樣咁有才華梗係高佬玩晒啦<br />\n俾你揀女兩個都白滑靚性格好 但一個大波一個無波<br />\n係人都識揀大波啦<br />\n仲有用明星做例子根本不切實際<br />\n因為fans同明星根本唔係現實中相處 成日係電視電腦望同現實望對高同矮個距離感都差好遠"},{"pid":"6ebd71285c0bf10323ca907b988a5bbb2744451f","tid":97642,"uid":63266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:02:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係笑死人<br />\n兩個都一樣咁有才華梗係高佬玩晒啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">俾你揀女兩個都白滑靚性格好 但一個大波一個無波<br />\n係人都識揀大波啦</span><br />\n仲有用明星做例子根本不切實際<br />\n因為fans同明星根本唔係現實中相處 成日係電視電腦望同現實望對高同矮個距離感都差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0ee0fb3cfcea0e67eebf7efec5669312a053bc","tid":97642,"uid":79275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係笑死人<br />\n兩個都一樣咁有才華梗係高佬玩晒啦<br />\n<span style=\"